data.description: This is not a drive-by you must see inside to appreciate the size and space this home has to offer. Large addition was done in 2008 doubling the size of this home. This home offers a large 2.5 acre lot with trees and level ground. Large deck and patio space to enjoy the privacy this yard has to offer. Lots of updates including Furnace-water heater, water softener, well pump and a NEW septic in 2019, New windows installed 2023. Home offers room for everyone! Lower level has a large den that could be a 6th bedroom or home office.
